897
01:34:10.400 --> 01:34:12.335
Credeam ca nu-ai
dezvalui secretele.

898
01:34:16.639 --> 01:34:18.675
Pana acum. nu.

899
01:34:28.952 --> 01:34:30.253
anca o tipa simpatica.

900
01:34:49.139 --> 01:34:50.707
