pana la decesul acestora.

903
01:34:55.378 --> 01:34:57.313
De aceea nu aai gasit
nimic an calculator.

904
01:34:57.380 --> 01:35:00.083
Care a fost motivul?

905
01:35:00.150 --> 01:35:03.119
