ca ea a comis crima.

920
01:35:59.442 --> 01:36:01.511
Despre care vorbim acum. Hoss?

921
01:36:01.578 --> 01:36:04.781
atim ca Hazel a comis o crima.
La fel ai Roxy.

922
01:36:04.848 --> 01:36:06.249
