928
01:36:41.718 --> 01:36:45.588
A spus ca Lisa Oberman
anvaaa aici an acel an.

929
01:36:48.224 --> 01:36:49.859
Am gasit o Tramell.

930
01:36:53.630 --> 01:36:54.931
Dar nici o Lisa Oberman.

931
01:36:54.998 --> 01:36:57.567
Sunteai sigura?
Nu poate fi o greaeala?

932
01:36:59.169 --> 01:37:01.671
Daca exista. greaeala
va aparaine. dle detectiv.

933
01:37:16.252 --> 01:37:18.855
Hazel. el este Nick.
ai-am povestit despre el.

934
01:37:18.922 --> 01:37:21.024
Nick. dansa e Hazel Dobkins.

935
01:37:21.090 --> 01:37:23.259
Tu eati "pistolarul". nu-i aaa?

936
01:37:23.326 --> 01:37:25.295
Ce mai faci?

937
01:37:25.361 --> 01:37:28.031
Bine. mulaumesc.
Putem vorbi puain?

938
01:37:28.097 --> 01:37:32.669
Aateapta-ma an maaina. te rog.
Vin imediat.

939
01:37:33.736 --> 01:37:35.672
La revedere. "pistolarule".

940
01:37:37.140 --> 01:37:39.943
aai place cumva
compania criminalilor?

941
01:37:40.009 --> 01:37:43.179
- atii ca Roxy a fost implicata an...
Da. bineanaeles ca atiam.

942
01:37:43.246 --> 01:37:46.149
Scriu carai despre oameni neobianuiai
iar uneori. an timpul documentarii

943
01:37:46.216 --> 01:37:48.618
intru ai an intimitatea lor.

944
01:37:48.685 --> 01:37:51.121
S-a antamplat ai an cazul tau.

945
01:37:52.355 --> 01:37:55.191
Crima nu e
ca fumatul.

946
01:37:55.258 --> 01:37:57.594
Te poai lasa.

947
01:37:59.796 --> 01:38:02.165
