952
01:38:15.411 --> 01:38:18.548
De ce?
Am spus "Hoberman".

953
01:38:21.251 --> 01:38:25.221
"Hoberman".
Lisa Hoberman cu "H".

954
01:38:26.790 --> 01:38:28.725
Serios?

955
01:38:30.693 --> 01:38:33.530
Bine.
Mulaumesc foarte mult.

956
01:38:35.431 --> 01:38:39.302
atii ca aa putea avea necazuri
mari pentru ce fac acum.

957
01:38:39.369 --> 01:38:40.590
Nici n-ar trebui sa fii aici.
an primul rand.

958
01:38:40.591 --> 01:38:41.704
Termina. Sam.

959
01:38:41.771 --> 01:38:44.340
Nu dureaza mult.

960
01:38:53.149 --> 01:38:54.984
Arata-mi fiaierul.

961
01:38:57.620 --> 01:39:00.123
E dna dr Garner. nu?

962
01:39:02.125 --> 01:39:04.727
Arata-mi 1983.

963
01:39:21.678 --> 01:39:23.746
N-ar trebui sa laai
uaa descuiata.

964
01:39:25.782 --> 01:39:28.618
N-am lasat-o.
Yala are ceva.

965
01:39:28.685 --> 01:39:30.086
Ce vrei?

966
01:39:30.153 --> 01:39:31.488
Povesteate-mi despre Catherine.

967
01:39:34.290 --> 01:39:36.860
Deci ai-a spus.

968
01:39:36.926 --> 01:39:39.829
Ce anume?

969
